================================================================================
claude-agent-sdk-cpp - C++ Port of Claude Agent SDK
================================================================================

Copyright 2025 Elias Bachaalany

This software is a C++ port of the claude-agent-sdk-python library.

This project is an independent, unofficial port and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Anthropic, PBC.

Original Work:
  claude-agent-sdk-python - Python SDK for Claude Agent
  Copyright (c) 2025 Anthropic, PBC
  Repository: https://github.com/anthropics/claude-agent-sdk-python
  License: MIT License

C++ Port:
  Author: Elias Bachaalany
  Repository: https://github.com/0xeb/claude-agent-sdk-cpp

Attribution (appreciated):
  If you find claude-agent-sdk-cpp useful, attribution is appreciated:
  "Uses claude-agent-sdk-cpp (https://github.com/0xeb/claude-agent-sdk-cpp) by Elias Bachaalany"

This C++ port is a complete reimplementation providing:
  - Native C++ performance
  - Header-only core components
  - Modern C++17/20 features
  - Cross-platform support (Windows, Linux, macOS)
  - Additional features: Session storage, template-based MCP API

================================================================================
